  <brief_title>Immunogenicity, Safety and Tolerability of Two Doses of a Pre-pandemic Influenza Vaccine in Participants Aged 6 Months to 17 Years</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Randomized, Controlled, Observer-blind, Single-center Study to Evaluate the Immunogenicity, Safety and Tolerability of Two Doses of an H5N1 Influenza Vaccine in Subjects Aged 6 Months to 17 Years</official_title>
  <sponsors>
